    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027970/extras/b0adba1c39947b653eb1927e8173ad29.poster.avif?t=1724844648\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027970/extras/b0adba1c39947b653eb1927e8173ad29.webm?t=1724844648\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027970/extras/b0adba1c39947b653eb1927e8173ad29.mp4?t=1724844648\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Neon Phonk Robots 是一款适合 Phonk 及其美学的真正鉴赏家的游戏。沉浸在这种音乐的动态氛围中，享受明亮的霓虹灯的光芒，炸毁更多的机器人！<br><br><strong>购买无人机</strong><br>您可以购买武装机器人！组建自己的机械同伴小队。你喜欢撕扯和投掷吗？创建一群冲锋队！你喜欢远距离消灭敌人吗？一群远程机器人将帮助您实现这一目标！您是否认为自己比别人聪明，并想组建一支平衡的小队？如您所愿！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027970/extras/d525ab648b8f514f7831cca1d38bba74.poster.avif?t=1724844648\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027970/extras/d525ab648b8f514f7831cca1d38bba74.webm?t=1724844648\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027970/extras/d525ab648b8f514f7831cca1d38bba74.mp4?t=1724844648\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>各种武器</strong><br>您可以购买新枪！厌倦了用冲锋枪炸毁机器人？买一支步枪！还有酸炮和几挺机枪！去炸毁机器人吧！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027970/extras/c7eb66f4e99c7e706df8878713d1d6ec.poster.avif?t=1724844648\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027970/extras/c7eb66f4e99c7e706df8878713d1d6ec.webm?t=1724844648\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027970/extras/c7eb66f4e99c7e706df8878713d1d6ec.mp4?t=1724844648\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>占领和加强点</strong><br>您可以占领点并购买炮塔！您占领了一个点吗？做得好，现在在上面安装一个健康的霓虹灯炮塔！让所有人都知道这是你的要点，你不会把它给任何人！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027970/extras/a2cca8b87ef0d8748a0461927bc70086.poster.avif?t=1724844648\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027970/extras/a2cca8b87ef0d8748a0461927bc70086.webm?t=1724844648\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027970/extras/a2cca8b87ef0d8748a0461927bc70086.mp4?t=1724844648\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>特定设计</strong><br>霓虹灯，霓虹灯，更多的霓虹灯！游戏真的像夜晚的东京一样闪闪发光！一切都在发光！墙壁、涂鸦、机器人、枪支、子弹，一切！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027970/extras/8e7a5c1675fe87947a75d70ad6563b97.poster.avif?t=1724844648\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027970/extras/8e7a5c1675fe87947a75d70ad6563b97.webm?t=1724844648\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027970/extras/8e7a5c1675fe87947a75d70ad6563b97.mp4?t=1724844648\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>独特曲目</strong><br>当你炸毁机器人时，最好听什么 - 当然是 Phonk。听 Phonk 时最好做什么？炸毁机器人！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027970/extras/81a3080d279d5b6dafde4eee135e55d7.poster.avif?t=1724844648\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027970/extras/81a3080d279d5b6dafde4eee135e55d7.webm?t=1724844648\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027970/extras/81a3080d279d5b6dafde4eee135e55d7.mp4?t=1724844648\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>你还在等什么？在 Neon Phonk Robots 中，将 phonk 开到最大，跑向霓虹城市，炸毁机器人！！！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027970/extras/10025e6dc88d14f0a1e99f69dcc98123.poster.avif?t=1724844648\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027970/extras/10025e6dc88d14f0a1e99f69dcc98123.webm?t=1724844648\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027970/extras/10025e6dc88d14f0a1e99f69dcc98123.mp4?t=1724844648\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
